OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly fine. Brightest early
OL,6,Fon, with some warm sunny spells and
OL,7,Flight winds, although cloud amounts
OL,8,Fgenerally increasing as the day
OL,9,Fprogresses, with rain spreading
OL,10,Fnorthwards by late afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIncreasingly cloudier
OL,13,Fovernight as band of rain,
OL,14,Foccasionally heavy, moves northwards
OL,15,Fthrough the region. Light easterly
OL,16,Fwinds but breezy along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
