OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA dry start becoming cloudy
OL,6,Fwith showers develop during the
OL,7,Fafternoon, some of which could be
OL,8,Fheavy at times. A breezy southeasterly
OL,9,Fwind will veer northwesterly later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBank
OL,12,Fholiday Monday, cloudier than
OL,13,Frecently, with some rain or showers.
OL,14,FTuesday and Wednesday will see
OL,15,Fsunshine and showers. Breezy along the
OL,16,Fcoast. Feeling a little cooler than of
OL,17,Flate.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
